ance Criteria**:\n42: - `TargetPort` struct compiles without errors\n43: - `Port` field has `+kubebuilder:validation:Minimum=1` and `+kubebuilder:validation:Maximum=65535` markers\n44: - `Protocol` field has `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS` marker\n45: - JSON tags are correctly formatted\n46: \n47: ---\n48: \n49: ### [ ] TASK-003: Define PodTemplateSpec helper type\n50: **Description**: Create `PodTemplateSpec` struct with metadata and spec fields.\n51: \n52: **Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n53: \n54: **Requirements**:\n55: - `Metadata metav1.ObjectMeta` - optional field\n56: - `Spec PodSpec` - optional field\n57: - Reuses Kubernetes core v1 types\n58: \n59: **Verification**:\n60: ```bash\n61: go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestPodTemplateSpec\n62: ```\n63: \n64: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n65: - `PodTemplateSpec` struct compiles without errors\n66: - Fields reference Kubernetes core v1 types correctly\n67: - JSON tags use camelCase\n68: \n69: ---\n70: \n71: ### [ ] TASK-004: Define AgentRuntimeSpec\n72: **Description**: Create `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct with all required fields and default values.\n73: \n74: **Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n75: \n76: **Requirements**:\n77: - `MaxSessionDuration string` - default \"8h\"\n78: - `SessionTimeout string` - default \"15m\"\n79: - `TargetPort []TargetPort` - minimum 1 item required\n80: - `PodTemplate PodTemplateSpec` - required field\n81: - Default value markers: `+kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"` and `+kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"`\n82: \n83: **Verification**:\n84: ```bash\n85: go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestAgentRuntimeSpec\n86: ```\n87: \n88: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n89: - `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct compiles without errors\n90: - Default value markers are correctly applied\n91: - Required fields are properly tagged\n92: - `TargetPort` has `+kubebuilder:validation:MinItems=1` marker\n93: \n94: ---\n95: \n96: 